# Architecture Decision Records Index

Architectural decisions are split by domain.

## ADR Sets

- [API ADR index](api/ADR-INDEX.md)
- [Frontend ADR index](frontend/ADR-INDEX.md)
- [Platform ADR index](platform/ADR-INDEX.md)

## Numbering Policy

- ADRs are numbered independently within each domain directory.
- New ADRs must be added to the appropriate domain index.

## Status Definitions

- **Proposed**: Under discussion.
- **Accepted**: Approved and implemented.
- **Deprecated**: No longer recommended.
- **Superseded**: Replaced by another ADR.
